dct_title_s: Carte du Détroit de la Maire : dressée sur les Journaux des Navigateurs
dct_description_sm: Map of the strait between Tierra Del Fuego and Staten Id. Relief shown pictorially and by bathymetric soundings. Prime meridians: Paris and Ferro. In lower margin: Tome XI. in 4⁰ no. 5; Tome 16 in 8̋⁰ page 154. Probably issued in: Histoire générale des voyages ... Paris : Didot, 1746-1789.
